    <tr ><td class="block_text" valign="top" align="left">Spaceregents is a FREE Massive Online Space Strategy Browser Game.<br />Hundreds of Players can play Spaceregents simultaneously via their Browsers and compete against each other.<br /><br />A SVG Browser Plugin is required, to view the map.<br /><br />The game is turned based. Each full hour a turn is over and movements, combats, constructions etc. are being made.<br />24 Hours a day, 7 Days a week. (hopefully ;)<br /><br />The <strong>goal</strong> of the game is to gain might.<br />To become the ruler of the galaxy you must outgrow your enemy.<br /><br />You can colonize all of the <strong>ten different types of planets</strong> in Spaceregents, build up an huge fleet and invade or simply destroy enemy colonies.<br /><strong>Trade</strong> your resources with your allies, friendly, neutral or even enemy alliances.<br /><br />Crush their neck using <strong>Covert Operation</strong>.<br />Surprise them by jumping in Zero-Time in enemy terrain, using the very expensive and password protected <strong>jumpgates</strong>.or simply order your Fleets to use the classic type of transportation: Warp-Speed.<br /><br /><strong>Dont be stupid, join an alliance</strong>. Else youll be blind, as you can only see, what your scanners and your allied scanners can catch.<br />Benefit from alliance development aid and become a minister or be elected to leader.</td></tr>
